News Leak

Description

A news platform where the admin appears to be hiding sensitive information.

Initial Exploration

The site displays articles such as:

/article.php?articleid=1

Testing invalid parameters produces database-related errors, indicating MongoDB usage.

Login Bypass (NoSQL Injection)

Login request was vulnerable to NoSQL injection.

Payload used:

username[$ne]=aaaa&password[$ne]=bbbb

This bypasses authentication and returns a valid session cookie.

Privilege Escalation

After login:

Comment functionality becomes available

Admin-only functionality is suspected

Testing revealed:

/admin.php

The admin login is vulnerable to the same NoSQL injection.

Admin Access

Using NoSQL injection again:

Admin session cookie is obtained

Access to /admin.php is granted

Although the page appears empty, inspecting the raw HTTP response reveals the flag stored in cookies.
